REQUEST VOCAB :

	      1. GET => request a resource from the server (html website, text, data etc.)

	      2. POST => sending resource to the server (form to Sign-Out a website)

	      |- 3. PUT => replace a resource (Replace the full thing)
UPDATE	| 
	      |- 4. PATCH => patch up a resource (relace and patch the damage part)

	      5. DELETE => Delete resources
